	head
		title MHacks
		meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1')
		style
			body {
				color:@blue;	
				background: url("http://www.mhacks.org/img/texture.png") repeat center;
				font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
			}
			.container {
				margin: 20px;
			}
	body
		.container
			h2 Hello #{name}! 
			h2 Thank you for signing up for mHacks!

			p We'll see you on February 1-3, 2013 at 
				a(href="https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msa=0&msid=213641796391042690596.0004867c348a1f7a831a9&ie=UTF8&ll=42.282048,-83.733737&spn=0.002056,0.003916&t=m&z=17&vpsrc=0&iwloc=0004867c348c607831eba&f=d&daddr=Palmer+Dr+%4042.280286,-83.733743")
					| Palmer Commons
				|  in Ann Arbor.
			p If you're coming from out-of-state please reach out us at 
				a(href='mailto:hackathon@umich.edu?Subject=Transportation%20to%20MHacks%20Inquiry') hackathon@umich.edu
				|  for transportation help. 
				| <br> We're doing our best to provide free transportation to all who come.

			
			p Stay tuned for more updates as we get closer to the event.

			h4 In the mean time please join our 
				a(href="http://www.facebook.com/groups/mhacks/") facebook group
				|  meant just for hackers to share ideas and ask questions about the event.
			
			
			p Lastly take a moment to invite your friends to 
				a(href="http://www.mhacks.org") mHacks
				|  by sharing our website! 
			br
			p Happy Hacking, 
			p The mHacks Team <br>
				a(href='mailto:hackathon@umich.edu?Subject=Transportation%20to%20MHacks%20Inquiry') hackathon@umich.edu
					
						
			.about
						
				